assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb9831d7f41f69d016594dfc814fb712736d5a6","tid":615610,"uid":38523,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"032ecbff36d26d501f0ae51105195fab4c41eee4","tid":615610,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁點<br />\ndisprove唔到以前賣港啲衰嘢<br />\n建立信任要做10件好事<br />\n破壞只需要1件</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"你冇資格講呢句啦<br />\n你自己買中資股比人屌時<br />\n你有冇打呢句野屌你自己啊<br />\n等緊你解釋你所謂泛民保皇狗一樣架<br />\n你打恬段野出來唔係解釋來架wo<br />\n而且<br />\n照你呢個道理<br />\n保皇狗直頭做十件衰野<br />\n先做半件好野啦<br />\n但又唔見你屌保皇狗好似屌泛民沚落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fb8eb92a52ee0128233b0a0081ff3aa490f7ef","tid":615610,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啲五毛平時喺各台表現正常<br />\n關鍵時刻叫人投保蝗<br />\n選舉後講句支持香港獨立<br />\n唔通樓進泛民打手又信咩？<br />\n弱智?定當人弱智?</span>"},{"pid":"434c990f4d6f73c430da8c96fbddafc32ac95363","tid":615610,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中資股愛好者保皇狗打手闔愛座hunter又開始想帶入其他話題"},{"pid":"bd66bc86e90ed7d2e3a499ad1a060e609a716551","tid":615610,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05fb8eb92a52ee0128233b0a0081ff3aa490f7ef","tid":615610,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啲五毛平時喺各台表現正常<br />\n關鍵時刻叫人投保蝗<br />\n選舉後講句支持香港獨立<br />\n唔通樓進泛民打手又信咩？<br />\n弱智?定當人弱智?</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"關鍵時刻叫人投保蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你關鍵時刻叫人投白票<br />\n就結果來講咪一樣<br />\n不過題外話來<br />\n唔好轉移視線<br />\n又話一樣既<br />\n但點解又唔係咁<br />